headline: UPS price target raised to $135 from $134 at JPMorgan

headline: UPS Completes Acquisitions of Healthcare Cold-Chain Logistics Providers Frigo-Trans and BPL
summary: ATLANTA, January 08, 2025--UPS (NYSE: UPS) today announced that it has completed the acquisition of Frigo-Trans and its sister company BPL, which provide industry-leading, complex healthcare logistics solutions across Europe.
